# CandelaRolls Environment Variables

This file lists the environment variables required for the CandelaRolls application.
Do not commit this file directly to version control. Use it as a template to create your own `.env.local` file.

# Base URL for the application
# In development, this is typically your ngrok URL or localhost:3000
# Example: NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://your-ngrok-subdomain.ngrok.io
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Stripe API Keys
# Get these from your Stripe Dashboard (Developers -> API keys)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_YOUR_STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_YOUR_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY # Used by frontend

# Stripe Webhook Secret
# Get this from your Stripe Dashboard (Developers -> Webhooks -> Add endpoint)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_YOUR_STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SIGNING_SECRET
